Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.36,0:00:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.61,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, the family won't have\N anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shout! It's almost time. {sounds like "scout" here but all the other sources give his name as シャウト}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.66,0:00:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,10, 9, 8, 7,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Shut up, won't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.25,Overlap,,0,0,0,,When it's time go, I'll start on my own cue.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,6, 5...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, whatever you say.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.42,0:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.63,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt your deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a garbage collector!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What gang are you from?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They stole our goods!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.07,0:00:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not thieves!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.07,0:00:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just throwing useless things away. {/unwanted }
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.74,0:01:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Floor it, Crunch! {kuranchi}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.25,0:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's them, the Midnight Trash Throw Away-ers, who can throw anything away?! {???? again took this name from MAL description, they were cooking, but still no clue what's that "bureedo" in the middle; I suspect it could be "Trail" from the show's title - that's what they call their trailer, but "trail throw awayers" doesn't sound good so I took another word from the title}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The grimoire is in place. {lit: magical tome}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.14,0:01:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tension, max!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.26,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One pull on this rope \Nwill get rid of magic for good! {/throw away}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become just an ordinary girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.45,0:01:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd shatter the grimoire \Nto pieces for sure this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.74,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really resistant to conventional methods?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter. I won't resort to magic!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.63,0:01:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, don't come! \NDon't come after me! Please! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I so wish I could throw this grimoire away.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. I won't forget it. {lit: I'll take it home}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.32,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one of our sisters sets out tonight. {lit: witch's daughter}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.74,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be schooled in the ways of a bride \Nwhile sharpening her witchcraft.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... To throw it away!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.58,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me all the info about how to throw it away.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna take ages \Nif I don't narrow my search down!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to throw it away.\NWhy is it so hard?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.09,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not thieves! \NWe're just throwing useless things away.{0:51}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They throw things away?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Makina, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for your ritual.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.11,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! I was just making sure \NI didn't forget anything, Madam Bishop! {shikyo-sama}{lit: I'll properly leave}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.70,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Makina, by tradition, on the night \Nof the first full moon after you turn 16,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.58,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be sent to the human world \Nto train in magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the guidance of a senior witch \Nwaiting for you there,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,collect all the passing marks \Nin your grimoire before returning.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't go, after all{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.75,0:03:17.76,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Out of the question!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't need magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be childish!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.68,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is human money. You're supposed\N to know how to use it by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Study well and don't waste any.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,I don't care about magical training.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.73,0:03:37.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,I wanna go into the human world, \Nbut only to be a normal girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.44,0:03:39.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,Magic be damned.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,Magic be damned.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,Magic be damned!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, fellow humans!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah, yikes! I'm supposed \Nto keep it a secret that I'm a witch.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry! I have money, see?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.14,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So stylish, so cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.14,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Swell! It's more exciting \Nthan flying on a broom!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm full!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.45,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I sure wonder why humans \Nwant to use money so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be so much easier with magic!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I made up my mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.96,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There are billions of humans on this earth, \Nand not even a thousand witches.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.34,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll try my best to become\N a normal human girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,An ice cream truck!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have twenty tea-flavored ones. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.64,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have chocolate and pineapple, also orange, milk, strawberry, and chocolate mint... Three of each!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam! Ice cream!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.23,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, young lady. These last customers just bought up the rest of my stock.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.32,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.87,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You, humans #1 and #2!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you buy it like that? \NWhy so much?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.16,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any restraint?! \NIce cream! Ice cream! Ice cream!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.84,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat it just for show!\NAnd it looked really delicious! {to make a display of; to show off; to flaunt}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.47,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We bought it and paid for it. \NGot any problem with...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to eat it, \Nthe stuff of my dreams, ice cream.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I burned through my money \Nand only have three pounds left.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.27,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to eat some ice cream, \Nand then you...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.03,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone! Where'd you go?! There you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you! If it comes to this...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.33,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to run, so my magic... \NI mean, karma caught up with you! {actually "divine punishment" (usually a lightning bolt) but I couldn't fit it into 20 cps}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, our bad. So, what now? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Trash Throw Away-ers?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.60,0:07:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}are{\i0} the Trash Throw Away-ers, all right, \Nbut we're different from ordinary garbage collectors.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you throwing away, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.44,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, there are quite a few things\N that you want to throw away, but can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.53,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,From your ex-lover's past secrets{ that you don't want to know}, \Nto large companies' confidential files, to state secrets.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you throw this away, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you throw it away, \NI'll forgive you for the ice cream.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.96,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.51,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. That's why I can't throw it away myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.60,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe if you flung it into \Nyour machine with the teeth... {lit: thing that does gagaga (clunking)}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I just knew, somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.65,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.36,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The children will copy you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we drop it from this height, \Nit'll shatter for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.13,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice. Show it to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna cost you, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really need to throw it away, \Ncome here at this time. It's our job.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll get rid of it for good.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.30,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like that escalated rather quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice pendant you have.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.89,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting. \NWhere have you been, Makina?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about you from Madam Bishop.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dorothy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been living among humans \Nfor who-knows-how-many years.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get married?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to a very handsome man.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.71,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal marriage, and a normal life...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not normal, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.17,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also sent to train in witchcraft \Nin the human world when I was young.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard to live hiding magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.22,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that, do you happen to know \Nof any good work for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.72,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent so much money in the human world, \NI'm in a bit of a pickle now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.52,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll show you a job that'll help\Nwith your witchcraft training.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care about that training!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to work normally \Nand live a normal life!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the question.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so blunt.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the witches' laws.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Laws?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At the height of the witch trials 500 years ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the great witch cursed those \Nwho fail to master witchcraft fully.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be turned into a frog.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A f-frog?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.05,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.72,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches are destined to learn witchcraft \Nand marry only demons. {akuma}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.68,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who rebel against it get turned \Ninto tree frogs{雨蛙}, toads{蟇}, bullfrogs{牛蛙}, and so on.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna be turned? {??? hikkurikaeru is "to fall down; to tumble down; to topple over; to lie on one's back" but idk what she means, maybe it's a pun on some frog name (frog = gaeru), maybe on "to turn into (kaeru)", commenting on the fact she fell down on her back}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.31,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything... but a frog... Anything... {/frog, frog}{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.19,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who were the two men \NI saw you with?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.07,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, just some friends I met by chance.\NOr should I say, "My ice cream rivals"?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you realize it too?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.66,0:10:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's pendant was a magical item.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.59,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a witch, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell, you knew?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.34,0:11:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches are so dangerous that the government \Neven keeps top-secret files on them!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the police has been on the move lately!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.02,0:11:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I don't mean to sound rude, \Nbut if we get involved with that girl{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.35,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still our customer,\Neven though she wants to throw away her grimoire. {/It doesn't change the fact she's ...}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she even have any money?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter. We'll get our due.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.07,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Training, training! Training!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Clairvoyance is my magic specialty!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It lets you avoid danger and keep one step ahead by reading people's mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm unbeatable at rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.25,0:11:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick to predicting the future is to use your nose. \NYou can read the air around you by smelling it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We start with the nostril-stretching machine. {/hole}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also part of your training. \NBear with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, your nostrils! We need to widen them!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.98,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? \NDoes it suit me, Madam Dorothy?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my debut as a human girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.03,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to pay for the clothes \Nwith your part-time job earnings.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's show you some applied witchcraft.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.87,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches shine in areas \Nthat humans have no idea about.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Resurrection magic can help a flower shop.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.09,Radio,,0,0,0,,There will be rain tomorrow. I guarantee it! {??? can't realyl hear her, but the seven day shows rain in the forecast}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.92,0:12:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Making it rain at will can help a weather forecaster.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ride your broom to do delivery work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.22,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches go to great lengths \Nto keep magic hidden from humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic that helps people?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you using your magic to help, Madam Dorothy?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.31,Overlap,,0,0,0,,You'll know when the time comes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as for your part-time job...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? {hai}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this restaurant.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Seriously?! {/so suddenly}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not really good at serving customers...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,More confidence! {??? probably "don't act spoiled/like a child"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are six of you, right? This way, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.75,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, there's only two...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're late! Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.13,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! 2, 3, 4, 5, 6. How...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. What do you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Customers need more time for that. {says "this kind of customers" for some reason}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish and chips, and a hamburger.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.26,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll have a mellow-flavored hamburger \Nwithout pickles, and Stroganoff. {I hear "maroyaka hanbagu" and maroyaka usually means "mellow (flavour, voice, etc.); mild; smooth​" but idk what to make of it when applied to burgers, probably means that it's not spicy?}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.02,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And for you, traditional chicken and green onion salt pasta without green onions, right? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing! She guessed it! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Start taking the order, manager. {/take a note/write it down}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.90,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Right... Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you'll have...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,Clairvoyance can be useful, actually!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Madam Dorothy!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Makina.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.87,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you... I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothy said she'd be working late tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.30,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't mind me. I'm on a diet.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothy's husband is so gentlemanly.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could also find a normal man like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Giggle? {uhihi - probably laughter}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't pretend any longer! {??? maybe something about soul, maybe something about keeping quiet}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.69,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothy didn't say it at first, \Nbut our eating habits are rather vulgar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Ah, excuse me, I gotta run now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.58,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna marry a demon. \NAnd I don't wanna turn into a frog either!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.42,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Absolutely no!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna throw it away.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.31,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna throw magic away!\NI don't wanna be a witch! {uses mahoutsukai here = "magic user" in general}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.94,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could throw the grimoire away, \NI'd be free to do whatever I want!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.57,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This way. No, this way! \NCome on, right here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.08,0:14:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to bus line O53 at 0:53!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup! We'll make sure to throw it away tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that! \NI thought it was magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean our camouflage? {lit: hiding technique}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, throw it away already! You promised!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.68,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The special vehicle we're towing has a 2.05 million horsepower press
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and a 2,000-degree incineration capacity.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, it operates at 2,085 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give you a demo \Nof how professionals do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.15,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that, the fee for using our machine, \Nincluding fuel costs and tax...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the money. \NYou said you'd do anything to get rid of it, right? {can't really rememeber this but idk what else it could mean}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought you could help us out \Nwith our work a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the two special agents \Nwho can read minds? {?? sounds like it's supposed to be someone else but dorothy later says "it's us"}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we came as promised. {/no doubt about it.}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you deployed the guards \Naccording to my instructions?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.09,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, two armed droid policemen \Nare already waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The arrangement is perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch a special capture team on two targets. {literal}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this stealing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just garbage collecting.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we sneaking around, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're sneaky Throw Away-ers.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're counting on your one special power.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My special power? What is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.53,0:16:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right below us. \NThere doesn't seem to be any security, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're stealing this?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not thieves!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that's one distasteful painting.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Demon's Night Feast"? {akuma no yaen - probably referencing https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Witches%27_Sabbath_(The_Great_He-Goat) (majou no yaen in japanese)}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna steal {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it away!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.23,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine the owner wouldn't take kindly \Nto you throwing it away.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our client is the artist \Nwho painted this picture.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a plagiarized work \Nhe drew when he was younger.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.24,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to regret it and wants to get rid of it, \Nbut it's out of his reach now. {lit: now that it ended up in a someone else's hands, there's nothing he can do}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So now... You're going to throw it away?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a piece of their past \Nthey want to throw away.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.54,0:17:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A past they want to throw away...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,Makina!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even I have something like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! They're aiming at you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.34,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A Special Capture Team!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Police Speed Droids on special assignment!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're reading our minds!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be possible!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the clairvoyance squad here!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, how did it come to this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter, just run! {?? lit: it's alright, come with us}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the picture, about your job?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. They saved us the effort \Nof getting rid of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to worry about ourselves now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn right at that corner!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.20,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But the exit is straight ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen to what I say! {and turn right}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been read again!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, lady, why not use some magic?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just blow them up! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I want to throw it away!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} a witch, after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the droids to the eastern service entrance.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.73,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that! All droids \Nto the eastern service entrance!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Crunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the safest exit?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eastern service entrance.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.02,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.69,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't smell right!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then use your magic... {to break out}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the question!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we with bring you along, then?! {lit: there's no meaning is calling you}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.57,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Enough, Crunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If she wants to throw it away, \Nwe can't use it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone should be allowed \Nto throw something away. {no matter the circumstances}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we, \Nthe Throw Away-ers, take pride in.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you're right. So be it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Crazy Trail! {show's title}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened there?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.52,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! It seems they've read us \Nat the eastern service entrance too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be riding it with us! {lit: it's us who'll get to ride it - meaning makina ca'nt get on}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let me in!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're only after us. {/we're the ones being targeted}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, young lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to look cool? \NYou're riding a garbage truck!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw your life away \Nalong with your magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... {cho[tto]}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a target. Not a target.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta save them!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta shake them off!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we had magic on our side... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.28,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to turn back now! {??? sounds more like "hey, wait a moment" but that doesn't connect with the next lines}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Back? Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dead end!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look after yourself! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch all droids \Nfrom capture mode to attack mode.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacking is against regulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our job is only to gather data{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter! Just do what I say!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When even my magic doesn't help...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack mode. Attack mode. Attack mode.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.10,0:20:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack mode. Attack mode.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.86,0:20:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A dead end!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Stop... Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.65,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Makina!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No! {dame?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.72,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Makina?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay? Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.40,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All the droids disappeared \Nfrom the search screen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.41,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the processing team deal with it later.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return to headquarters.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.83,0:21:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That mole was Makina's familiar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that {\i1}Makina{\i0} was reading us?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.12,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up, Madam Witch?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shout?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved us.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.48,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a waste, throwing away such power?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm throwing it away!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.32,0:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to crush my grimoire\n with your truck, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroying that grimoire is beyond our power. {lit: we can't do it with our hands}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you'll have to give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.29,0:21:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.87,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now, Makina?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.00,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.59,0:22:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll look for some other place \Nto throw it away.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you {\i1}must{\i0} take me with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! You promised to rid me of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're still going on about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.56,0:22:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we should just let her go like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.19,0:22:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's also part of her training.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.61,0:22:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she's already better \Nat clairvoyance than me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.70,0:22:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I already got one passing mark in witchcraft!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.70,0:22:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that. You wanted to throw it away, \Nbut you leveled-up instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?! \NI'll throw it away! I absolutely will!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.16,0:22:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.08,0:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fussy customer.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.67,0:22:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Floor it! {/let it fly}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.55,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazily... {lit: in crazy - maybe refers to their trailer but idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With a spring! {???? poipoi is onomatopoeia for "tossing" but I think she means something closer to how skipping stones move, unless it's something different altogether}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.34,0:22:49.68,Radio,,0,0,0,,In other news,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.39,Radio,,0,0,0,,the artist of the damaged painting, "A Demon's Night Feast," has released a statement.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.39,0:22:56.56,Radio,,0,0,0,,"My sadness and indignation are immeasurable.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.56,0:23:02.52,Radio,,0,0,0,,However, my dissatisfaction over this incident \Nwill allow me to put my soul into my new work." {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.52,0:23:05.65,Radio,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the museum has offered compensation. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.80,0:23:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot about my familiar! {???? no clue what's this soubi, maybe the mole's name? lit: I left soubi behind}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.65,0:23:08.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,What a broad-minded person!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just bring him back with your magic. {??? lit: using magic is okay}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.11,0:23:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.86,Radio,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned for further details.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.49,0:23:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel so good...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.10,0:05:00.48,Song,,0,0,0,,{"mirai rail / ミライレイル" by the VA of Makina; somehow no lyrics on the internet, going by ear, duh}Nice to meet you, brand new world
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.48,0:05:05.49,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I can change too
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.49,0:05:13.45,Song,,0,0,0,,To be as colorful as everyone else
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.17,0:05:23.46,Song,,0,0,0,,If I can see your smile
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.46,0:05:29.43,Song,,0,0,0,,I don't need anything else
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.43,0:05:36.44,Song,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye to the magic of the dreamy world
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.44,0:05:41.07,Song,,0,0,0,,I won't look back at my old memories
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.07,0:05:46.86,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll go beyond my memories and move on to a new me
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.53,Song,,0,0,0,,I know there's a future for me
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.53,0:05:56.29,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll meet somewhere
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.29,0:06:01.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Far away from here
